headline: BlackRock Elects Bayo Ogunlesi to Board of Directors
summary: NEW YORK, November 19, 2024--BlackRock, Inc. (NYSE: BLK) announced today that Adebayo ("Bayo") Ogunlesi, Founding Partner, Chairman and Chief Executive Officer of Global Infrastructure Partners ("GIP"), and a Senior Managing Director at BlackRock, has been elected to BlackRock’s Board of Directors ("Board").

headline: Bitcoin Hits All-Time High of $94,000 as Post-Election Rally Continues
summary: The price of Bitcoin hit a record high on Tuesday afternoon, continuing its dramatic ascent in the two weeks since Donald Trump’s victory in the presidential election.
